{"tid":1544001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張炳良：不可能不重啟政改討論","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T14:29:11.000Z","uid":212626,"like":162,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"46c7c074c45de0bfb5f526067d97c0dc31af1eba","tid":1544001,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:44:15.000Z","msg":"教育大學公共行政學研究講座教授、運輸及房屋局前局長張炳良在電台節目形容，現時社會像「自殘」，要使用破壞秩序影響機場等抗爭手段，<span style=\"color: red;\">如政府早在6月中宣布撤回修例，不少紛爭可以停下來，對此感到可惜</span>。<br />\n<br />\n張炳良指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">修例風波揭示香港深層次問題，年輕人不滿涉及選舉及權力問題，若要處理體制結構問題，不可能不重啟政改討論</span>，過程中或須討價還價，要看今次風暴後，各方會否以不同角度看待。<br />\n<br />\n至於特首提出與司局長走入社區對話，張炳良指有兩個變數，包括市民是否願意對話，第二是如<span style=\"color: red;\">市民覺得對話後仍無變化，或會帶來反效果</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2243676/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2243676%2F&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=00418fd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2243676/</a>"},{"pid":"fbbecf9413d9ba0a17b44dfc523d766732b3337a","tid":1544001,"uid":200288,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:45:09.000Z","msg":"無啦啦講人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e342abcb8ba23590c095d9acd63004102a381ced","tid":1544001,"uid":94828,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"fbbecf9413d9ba0a17b44dfc523d766732b3337a","tid":1544001,"uid":200288,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:45:09.000Z","msg":"無啦啦講人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:46:03.000Z","msg":"人之將死"},{"pid":"3bb2c7e0d218a5a3b31bdaf323bbc6febe8ea155","tid":1544001,"uid":279981,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:46:16.000Z","msg":"改你老母呀 又想我地袋著先 <br />\n做美國佬隻狗好過做大陸下等人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\